name: Distant Harbors - Galactic Krill
description: High up in the sky there is a sanctuary that creates lightning and thunder. It is built upon a fluffy cloud and is composed of high towers, hanging gardens and of course a lot of gears and pipes and all these things needed to kick up a fuss down here. If you ever wondered how to get there, here is the answer. Galactic Krill will pick you up in your dreams and bring you to distant harbors. If you wonder how it looks like up there, visit the hallway at https://nftblackmarket.io/market/trade/712
